Real CRUD mental model (used).





 PROJECT 6 (Day 12–13)
react-api-integration → Connect Real Backend
Now you connect to existing backend APIs.
Do NOT import old services.
Rewrite manually.
Create New Service File
src/services/productService.js
Write fetch logic using fetch() (not axios first).
Features
Load products from DB
Add product
Delete product
Handle loading properly
Handle API errors cleanly
 Skills This Builds
Frontend ↔ Backend understanding without copying.




